################
generate_phone_text.sh
###############

Converts character based text to phone based text. Look at the comments in the code for more information.

Execute the script as:
bash generate_phone_text.sh

################
phonify_words.sh
###############
Script to generate lexicon (phone-level transcriptions) for words in Indian languages

Input: text containing list of words (note that no special characters have to be present along with the words)
Outputs: (1) lexicon_cls: dictionary in common label set (2) lexicon_phone: dictionary wherein each CLS label is represented by a single UTF-8 character

Execute the script as:
bash phonify_words.sh <unique_words>
Ex: bash phonify_words.sh unique_words
